{"id":74363,"title":"Collaboration in translational neuroscience: a call to arms.","abstract":"Neurological and psychiatric disorders present an immediate and growing challenge. The scale and complexity of this unmet need calls for a concomitantly large and sophisticated response. Here the author discusses just one element of such a response, the power of collaboration, and presents a personal account of how a variety of collaborative structures can advance science. ","date":"2014-12-02","categories":"Nervous System Diseases","split":"test","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25442928","annotations":[{"name":"Neuroscience","weight":0.75072,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Neuroscience"},{"name":"Science","weight":0.706228,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Science"},{"name":"Disease","weight":0.536506,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disease"},{"name":"Mental disorder","weight":0.478001,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mental_disorder"},{"name":"Psychiatry","weight":0.439226,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Psychiatry"},{"name":"Author","weight":0.265779,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Author"},{"name":"Neurology","weight":0.189447,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Neurology"},{"name":"Complexity","weight":0.122139,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Complexity"},{"name":"Chemical element","weight":0.0311179,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chemical_element"},{"name":"Coat of arms","weight":0.0279596,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coat_of_arms"},{"name":"Power (philosophy)","weight":0.0279596,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Power_(philosophy)"},{"name":"Collaboration","weight":0.0276227,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Collaboration"},{"name":"Tertiary structure","weight":0.0265028,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tertiary_structure"},{"name":"M